description:
Peter and Gary explore the incredible achievement to evacuate thousands of men, horses and tonnes of equipment from the Anzac and Suvla sectors of Gallipoli in December 1915.

Presenters: Peter Hart and Gary Bain Publisher: Mat McLachlan Producer: Jess Stebnicki
